Dialogue: 5,0:01:56.60,0:02:01.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É isso aí, seu idiota!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:02.32,0:02:04.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se ele morrer, eu vou matar ele!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.71,0:02:08.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu cuido da sua retaguarda!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.59,0:02:13.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso aí, Gomu Gomu!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai lá, irmão Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:17.60,0:02:19.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você consegue!\NVocês estão no mesmo nível!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.82,0:02:22.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai pro inferno, verme!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Ele tem dentes novos!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.52,0:02:27.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou um tubarão. Dentes novos\Nnascem um atrás do outro.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:27.08,0:02:30.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E eles são mais resistentes\Ndo que os anteriores.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.25,0:02:34.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cada vez mais!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.25,0:02:38.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uau!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.09,0:02:42.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quantas vezes eu {\i1}quiser{\i0}!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:44.38,0:02:46.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esses são os traços que os céus nos concederam.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é incrível!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.15,0:02:53.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você está começando a perceber que\Nraça superior são os tritões?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.10,0:03:05.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tooth & Gum!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.58,0:03:08.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.73,0:03:14.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.09,0:03:21.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Irmão Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.05,0:03:21.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A-Arlong...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.97,0:03:27.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I-Isso doeu.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-Quê...! I-Irmão!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.99,0:03:50.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ufa.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.64,0:03:53.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seu desgraçado de borracha!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como ousa usar meu irmão\Ncomo escudo!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que você tá falando?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.30,0:04:02.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Foi você que atacou.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.24,0:04:07.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ufa... Aquilo deu um baita susto.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.22,0:04:09.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não se mova,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.00,0:04:11.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,seu desgraçado de borracha!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.18,0:04:14.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, é!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.30,0:04:18.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu tive uma ideia divertida.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.45,0:04:20.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma ideia divertida?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.05,0:04:22.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que será que ele vai fazer...?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele tem algum truque\Nna manga?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tooth & Gum!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.69,0:04:28.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pronto!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.66,0:04:31.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Idiota,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,é inútil você ficar\Ndestruindo meus dentes.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você ainda não entendeu?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I-Irmão Luffy,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.80,0:05:09.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,me diz que essa não é\Na sua ideia divertida.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olha! Eu também tenho presas!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Então ele não tinha nenhum\Ntruque na manga?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.44,0:05:19.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Até quando você vai
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,ficar brincando?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.68,0:05:30.64,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,O tubarão me mordeu!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É porque você fica brincando!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não tô tentando brincar.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.58,0:05:44.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tooth & Gum!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Arlong mordeu ele!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.99,0:05:50.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Gostou de provar do seu\Npróprio remédio? Dente por dente!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pode usar meus dentes o quanto quiser.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você ainda tá preso\Ncom essa mandíbula fraca.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.29,0:06:28.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Escuta aqui.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.80,0:06:32.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Os dentes de tubarão só servem\Ncom mandíbulas fortes,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.70,0:06:36.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,que rasgam a carne!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ahh! O braço do irmão\Nvai ser arrancado!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.31,0:06:43.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O braço dele tá bem?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.42,0:06:50.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se ele tivesse recuado um passo,\Nteria perdido o braço!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Duvido que ele pensou muito sobre o que as presas fariam com ele.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.20,0:07:37.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra onde ele foi?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.41,0:07:42.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy! O mar!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:03.05,0:08:04.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O mar?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tem um tubarão!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É o Arlong!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.79,0:08:09.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê? Ele mergulhou?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é sério!\NEle é duas vezes mais forte na água.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.06,0:08:16.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ninguém pode me parar quando\Neu ganho velocidade debaixo d'água.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.04,0:08:24.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa habilidade é justamente o tipo\Nconcedido apenas aos tritões.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.22,0:08:30.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele fugiu?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.31,0:08:38.41,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shark Gone...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.41,0:08:43.66,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Darts!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que foi aquilo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.69,0:09:00.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um torpedo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alguma coisa voou do mar!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ai! Ai, ai, ai, ai...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uau, você se saiu bem.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.36,0:09:18.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas quanto mais você desviar,\Nmais sofrimento vai ter.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.87,0:09:22.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shark Gone Darts!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.00,0:09:31.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-Que diabos os ossos daquele\Ntubarão maldito são feitos?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.63,0:09:36.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O nariz dele despedaçou o chão!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.93,0:09:42.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shark Gone Darts!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.31,0:09:54.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei Luffy, você precisa se esconder!\NO Arlong voltou pro mar!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Irmão! Por favor, se esconde logo!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.28,0:10:00.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele vai te mirar de novo!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.51,0:10:21.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sai daí!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.47,0:10:25.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Não.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.19,0:10:27.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não seja burro! Você tá querendo\Nser um alvo?! Se protege!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não quero! Eu vou pegá-lo\Ne quebrar o nariz dele!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.09,0:10:38.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pode vir, tubarão!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.20,0:10:43.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você tem coragem.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.89,0:10:48.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ou você percebeu que fugir\Nnão vai te salvar?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:48.46,0:10:51.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vocês não percebem que precisam\Nse esconder, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você mal desviou dos ataques,\Nmas todos te pegaram de raspão!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.69,0:11:00.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquele golpe te mata na hora\Nse você levar em cheio!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.47,0:11:04.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.98,0:11:08.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Escudo!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.99,0:11:13.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que postura é essa?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.14,0:11:15.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele não vai tentar parar\No ataque assim, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.02,0:11:20.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho o dobro de distância\Npra acelerar dessa vez!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou perfurar o seu coração!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shark Gone Darts!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Acertou em cheio!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.50,0:11:30.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espera, ele levou o golpe?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.10,0:11:34.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não! Ele se jogou pra longe!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Acabou pra você! Esse ataque\Nnão funciona mais.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.15,0:11:57.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shark Gone Darts!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.28,0:12:00.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seu desgraçado!\NFoi só um chute de sorte!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.98,0:12:05.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Este é o golpe final!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.98,0:12:09.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você não vai me acertar!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Rede!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.59,0:12:21.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pescaria! Eu tô pescando!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Lança!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.76,0:12:29.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uau!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm? Ele morreu?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O olhar do Arlong mudou!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.41,0:12:49.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele tá igualzinho aos reis do mar\Nquando partem pro ataque.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.21,0:12:57.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O último ataque do Luffy deve ter deixado ele furioso!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.71,0:13:02.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca vi o Arlong\Ncom aquele olhar.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.17,0:13:07.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Humano inferior!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que você pensa que\Nestá fazendo comigo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.18,0:13:16.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou um tritão!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.15,0:13:19.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cara, que susto!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não doeu,\Nmas ele tá definitivamente puto.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.06,0:13:27.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que diabo é aquilo?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.81,0:13:36.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kiribachi!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.88,0:13:41.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É uma serra monstruosa!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Irmão Luffy!\N– Aguenta firme, Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:53.14,0:13:54.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Corre! Cuidado!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.77,0:13:57.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O ataque é implacável.\NEle tá encurralado!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.13,0:14:22.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele fugiu pro prédio!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.09,0:14:25.09,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,É a janela esquerda no último andar.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.09,0:14:25.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquela sala é...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não tem mais pra onde fugir.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.42,0:14:44.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Este é o último andar do Arlong Park.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que sala é essa?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tá cheio de papéis.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.80,0:14:55.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não são papéis comuns.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esta é a sala onde eu faço aquela\Ngarota desenhar mapas. É...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,...a sala de cartografia!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.75,0:15:01.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A sala da Nami.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.87,0:15:06.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esses são os mapas marítimos\Nque a Nami desenhou.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.22,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,No mundo inteiro, poucos conseguiriam desenhar mapas tão precisos!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.79,0:15:11.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A garota tem um dom.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.40,0:15:15.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não há nada tão triste e absurdo
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.72,0:15:22.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,quanto desperdiçar um talento nato.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.34,0:15:26.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela vai encontrar a verdadeira felicidade\Nficando aqui e desenhando mapas!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esta caneta está manchada de sangue.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.80,0:15:38.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Os mapas da Nami são absolutamente vitais\Nse eu quiser dominar o mundo!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.39,0:15:44.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela vai continuar desenhando\Nmapas! Tudo pela minha ambição!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.00,0:15:47.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quando aprendermos tudo sobre os mares do mundo através desses mapas,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.88,0:15:53.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,nós tritões seremos invencíveis,\Ne meu império se espalhará pelo globo!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.55,0:16:01.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esta ilha e o East Blue\Nsão os trampolins pra esse fim!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.09,0:16:04.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como você poderia usá-la\Ntão eficientemente assim?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.69,0:16:10.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?! A Kiribachi...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.53,0:16:16.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,não se move!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.95,0:16:23.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.29,0:16:37.10,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,"Usar"?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.10,0:16:39.48,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,O que tá acontecendo lá dentro?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.97,0:16:46.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga! O que aconteceu,\Nirmão Luffy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não dá pra saber o que tá\Nacontecendo lá em cima.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.23,0:16:54.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.35,0:16:58.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que você acha que ela é pra você?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.48,0:17:02.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela é uma criatura inferior,\Nmas uma garota inteligente.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.19,0:17:06.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se comparar todos os outros humanos a ratos de esgoto,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.21,0:17:10.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,então ela é uma gatinha atrevida.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.45,0:17:15.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Afinal, ela é adorável.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.58,0:17:18.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E eu vou continuar alimentando ela\Ne comprando as roupas que ela gosta.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.30,0:17:21.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela vai ter tudo\Nque precisa pra viver.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.28,0:17:23.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tudo que ela precisa fazer é continuar\Ndesenhando mapas pra mim.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.20,0:17:29.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela vai ser minha ferramenta pra sempre...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.19,0:17:32.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,não, parte da minha tripulação.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.78,0:17:38.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que é aquilo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.41,0:17:43.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma mesa...?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.00,0:17:46.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,U-Ufa, é só uma mesa.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cara, que susto. Eu jurei\Nque era o irmão Luffy.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.79,0:18:00.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Calma aí, parceiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.71,0:18:04.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você tá dizendo que não tem fé\Nna força do irmão Luffy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.30,0:18:07.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quê...?!\NVocê também se assustou, Johnny!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.98,0:18:09.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Não seja idiota!\NEu tava, tipo, sabe...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.62,0:18:12.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Eu naturalmente achei\Nque era aquele maldito Arlong!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.94,0:18:16.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hã?! Parece que você tá tentando me enrolar!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.60,0:18:20.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fala sério, seu idiota! É claro que\No irmão Luffy nunca perderia!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.09,0:18:22.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:22.28,0:18:25.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que você pensa que tá fazendo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.39,0:18:30.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que diabos tá acontecendo?!\NUm monte de tralha voando pra todo lado!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.45,0:18:31.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo! A partir de hoje,\Neste é o seu quarto!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:33.34,0:18:35.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sua mesa, suas canetas...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.26,0:18:40.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tudo que você vai precisar tá aqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.06,0:18:53.70,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Para com isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.89,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Os mapas!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.89,0:18:59.03,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Meus mapas!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.99,0:19:04.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sua pirralha!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não pense que pode me enganar,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.49,0:19:10.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,desenhando mapas falsos assim!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.28,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Você tem tempo de ficar\Ndesenhando essa porcaria escondida?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.96,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Tente me enganar de novo, e eu vou arrastar pessoas do vilarejo uma por uma
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.68,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,e fazer você assistir enquanto eu torço o pescoço delas!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:22.10,0:19:25.76,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Elas vão ter o mesmo destino que ela!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.93,0:19:33.80,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Maldito! Eu passei oito anos\Nfazendo ela desenhar isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.80,0:19:36.29,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu investi oito anos nesses\Nmapas! Na minha ambição!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.29,0:19:38.19,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Bell-mère-san...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.24,0:19:45.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nojiko...!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.98,0:19:49.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa é uma luta bem intensa!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.30,0:19:55.36,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,É! Parece uma luta de vida ou morte!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.29,0:19:58.13,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Com certeza!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.34,0:20:06.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você foi longe demais,\Nseu monstro de borracha!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"Tritões são ótimos" e...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.79,0:20:20.53,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,"mapas" isso,\N"circunstâncias" aquilo...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.09,0:20:30.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não entendo muito\Ndessas coisas...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.60,0:20:35.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas eu finalmente descobri como salvá-la!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:35.39,0:20:38.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Este quarto é o motivo de ela\Nnão poder sair deste lugar!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:38.99,0:20:41.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela não quer ficar aqui,\Nentão eu vou destruir tudo!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.71,0:20:46.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.91,0:20:54.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não se atreva!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.90,0:20:59.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Escória como vocês nunca\Nconseguiriam destruir o Arlong Park!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.61,0:21:02.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shark Gone Cog!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.40,0:21:06.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Machado de Guerra!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.14,0:21:10.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-Olha o que aquele impacto\Nfez com o Arlong Park!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Impossível! Vai desabar!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.00,0:21:18.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é perigoso!\NTodo mundo, pra trás!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:01.17,0:22:04.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami! Rápido!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:05.59,0:22:07.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas o Luffy ainda tá lá dentro!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:07.21,0:22:09.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:10.30,0:22:11.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy! E o Luffy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:11.76,0:22:13.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:13.03,0:22:13.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:13.77,0:22:15.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:20.81,0:22:22.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:35.63,0:22:37.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que barulheira maldita é essa?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:46.84,0:22:48.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:00.60,0:23:05.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Arlong Park... desabou!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:05.10,0:23:08.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Irmão.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:12.81,0:23:14.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que diabos aconteceu lá dentro?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:27.17,0:23:30.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem venceu?!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:30.99,0:23:32.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Com todos esses destroços,\Nnão me diga que foi...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:32.88,0:23:36.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:36.90,0:23:38.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:38.59,0:23:42.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Irmão!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:43.20,0:23:44.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele tá bem?!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:55.37,0:23:56.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:56.47,0:24:00.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você é uma de nós!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:04.19,0:24:07.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Irmão!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:13.05,0:24:14.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele tá bem?!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:19.02,0:24:22.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:33.87,0:24:35.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sei!
